item.title: Design of flexible production line of circuit board of Wuhan University of Technology
item.description: Design of flexible production line of circuit board of Wuhan University of Technology. Flexible production line of circuit board is an intelligent flexible production line to product circuit board, which is developed based on a set of advanced manufacturing concept, the process of production includes intelligent production, processing, assembly, and warehousing, digital logistics tracking and so on.
